</li>
<li id="cite_note-20"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"> Pew Research Center, 
<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.pewforum.org/2019/12/16/the-digital-pulpit-a-nationwide-analysis-of-online-sermons/">The Digital Pulpit: A Nationwide Analysis of Online Sermons</a>, pewforum.org, USA, December 16, 2019</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-21"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Christina L. Baade, James Andrew Deaville, <i>Music and the Broadcast Experience: Performance, Production, and Audience</i>, Oxford University Press, USA, 2016, p. 300</span>
</li>
